[[Virgil|Vergil]], ''[[Aeneid]].'' Theodore C. Williams. trans. Boston. Houghton Mifflin Co. 1910. [http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/hopper/text?doc=Perseus%3Atext%3A1999.02.0054%3Abook%3D1%3Acard%3D1 Online version at the Perseus Digital Library.]\n\n==External links==\n*{{Commonscatinline}}\n\n{{Greek mythology (deities)}}\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Cretan mythology]]\n[[Category:Greek goddesses]]\n[[Category:Earth goddesses]]\n[[Category:Fertility goddesses]]\n[[Category:Mother goddesses]]\n[[Category:Offspring of Gaia]]\n[[Category:Titans]]\n[[Category:Rhea| ]]\n[[Category:Offspring of Oceanus]]\n[[Category:Mountain goddesses]]\n[[Category:Saturnian deities]]\n", "name_user": "Pratham456", "label": "vandal", "comment": "(\u2192\u200eEtymology)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rhea_(mythology)"}
